      • putAscii

        <T> T putAscii(String name,
               String context,
               EnumSet<PropagationMode> propagationModes)
        throws InsufficientCredentialException
        Store the specified work context under the specified name into the in-scope ContextMap.
        Parameters:
        name - The name to associate to the specified work context
        context - an ascii String work context.
        propagationModes - A set of propagation modes that control over which protocol this work context will be propagated.
        Returns:
        The work context being replaced.
        Throws:
        InsufficientCredentialException - If the user has insufficient privileges to access that work context.
